  "text": "The basic principle of micromachined cantilevers offers an interesting possibility to measure a variety of physical parameters [CITATION_1] . When used as a sensor, a MEMS structure requires the use of a sensing mechanism and the most widely used is the capacitive method. The moving structure, and a fixed plate, forms a parallel plate capacitor, where the structure movement is translated into a capacity change.",
